metadata.Plot: A married police captain arrives at a lake to watch the best meteor shower of the year. At a crossroads in his life, Adam gets an unexpected visit from an eccentric, single nurse. As the night progresses and the conversation gets deeper, Adam and Nicole realize the stars aren't the only things falling.
